data.description: One level, all brick 3/bd 2/ba ranch home in the heart of Columbia. Close to shopping and hospital. Huge kitchen with tons of storage space, granite counters with SS appliances (refrigerator stays) that is open to the large great room. Beautiful covered rocking chair front porch. Updated items include:  Newer Metal Roof, HVAC including new duct work, gutters with gutter guard and water heater. Partially fenced in back yard with 2 storage buildings that remain. Tons of closet space and storage. Wonderful established neighborhood.
